name: Butts and Bare Feet V1.0
description:
Welcome to Butts and Bare Feet.

Before using, consider the following:

  • I have only been in this space for a few days, be prepared for inconsistency on V1.0.

  • I am no lawyer, however ethically this LORA should never be used for profit, as it was trained on real people.

  • This LORA is very sensitive and adjusting the weight on the same seed is your friend. Using RV1.3, I found acceptable results on 0.3-0.4, 0.6, and 0.9. It also produces varying quality results at the beginning/end of the prompt.

  • Favorable to a 16:9 portrait orientation, such as 432x786.

  • Legs/toes are FUBAR'd in some cases, and require a future fix.

  • Lighting can be an issue.

  • I recommend using the Euler a sampling method.

If you'd like to help me out as I'm new to the space, or discuss, you can contact me on Discord. This is not yet a place to ask for assistance, as I'm still figuring out this space.

This is also compatible with Anime Checkpoints. Experiment!

Trigger prompts:

There will be more to add as I discover more about LORA.

Base prompt: kneeling, from behind

Kneeling locations: on bed, on floor, in chair, in office chair, on stool, in car, on couch

Prompt enhancements: ass spread, legs spread, thong, panties, no panties

Model used for training:

Realistic Vision V1.3
